title: GRID.Autosport.High.Res.Texture.Pack.Addon-HI2U
description:
HI2U!

GRID Autosport - High Res Texture Pack (c) Codemasters

Release Date : 27th of June, 2014
Protection   : Steam
Type         : Racing
Size         : 49 x 100mb

Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~

Download the all new high resolution texture pack, boosting your car textures
up to 4k resolution. To enable the High Res Textures, once installed simply
set your texture quality to high.

Install:
~~~~~~~

Unrar, mount/burn, install the texture pack to the dir where main game is
installed and play.
